lead_paragraph: Manchester United manager Jose Mourinho said the international break has made his plans for the Manchester derby a bit more "complicated" than he would have liked, especially with his South American players returning a day before the clash.

headline.print_headline: Mourinho Laments Timing of International Break for Derby
headline.main: Mourinho Laments Timing of International Break for Derby
